maintext: Ukrainian lawmaker, center, throws some object against parliament speaker Andriy Parubiy, top right, as other scuffle during a parliament session in the Ukrainian parliament, in Kiev, Ukraine, Friday, Oct. 6, 2017. The parliament was forced to adjourn its session amid scuffles over hotly-disputed bills regarding the rebel-controlled eastern territories. (AP Photo/Efrem Lukatsky)
